pacman::p_load(haven, dplyr, summarytools, sjmisc, car, sjlabelled, sjPlot, lme4, stargazer, corrplot, ltm, texreg, ordinal, MASS, webshot)
load("input/data/proc/data_rec.RData")
data_bienestar <- na.omit(data_rec)
data_bienestar <- data_bienestar %>% mutate(pension_rec = 5-just_pension,
                                            educ_rec = 5-just_educ,
                                            salud_rec = 5-just_salud)
data_bienestar <- data_bienestar %>% rowwise() %>% dplyr::mutate(bienestar = mean(c(educ_rec, salud_rec, pension_rec)))
data_bienestar$bienestar <- round(data_bienestar$bienestar, 2)

reg10.1_bienestar <- lmer(bienestar ~ 1 + esfuerzo_soc + merito_soc + inteligencia_soc + esfuerzo_esc + inteligencia_esc + educacion_rec + libros_rec + acc_tec + mean_educ + cod_depe2 + cod_grupo + simce + internet_rec + (1 | mrbd), data=data_bienestar)
